    ('Phomiliar', '../images/pho1.jpg', 'Vietnamese', 'Austin', 'TX', 'Award winning food and Pho soup are sure to satisfy all of the Pho-natics and first-timers alike. Don&#39;t take our word for it... Stop by one of their two locations!'),
