    ('Green Bridge', '../images/steak.jpg', 'American', 'Decatur', 'NE', 'The Green Bridge is a local landmark. Established in 1956 which burnt down in 1998 and Rebuilt by a group of investors to open in 1999. Come on in for some popcorn shrimp and a Shirley Temple!'),
    ('Dundee&#39;s', '../images/pub.jpg', 'Pub', 'Charlotte', 'SC', 'World famous Fish n Chips, Reuben sandwich, and Single Malt Scotch Wall! Bring family & friends for some good food, an array of beverages, and quirky people.'),
